多女性,为区域妇幼健康事业贡献更大力量。\nF·PAC(女性生殖健康促进)是一项公益项目,旨在通过规范化服务,帮助流产后女性树立科学避孕意识,保护生殖健康。\n如有相关需求,欢迎前来我院妇科咨询。', 'siteName': 'njsqxqyy.com', 'siteIcon': 'https://th.bochaai.com/favicon?domain_url=https://njsqxqyy.com/content/?644.html', 'datePublished': '2026-03-19T16:13:27+08:00', 'dateLastCrawled': '2026-03-19T16:13:27Z', 'cachedPageUrl': None, 'language': None, 'isFamilyFriendly': None, 'isNavigational': None}], 'someResultsRemoved': True}, 'images': {'id': None, 'readLink': None, 'webSearchUrl': None, 'value': [{'webSearchUrl': None, 'name': None, 'thumbnailUrl': 'https://njsqxqyy.com/upload/image/20260319/17739081171165448.png', 'datePublished': None, 'contentUrl': 'https://njsqxqyy.com/upload/image/20260319/17739081171165448.png', 'hostPageUrl': 'https://njsqxqyy.com/content/?644.html', 'contentSize': None, 'encodingFormat': None, 'hostPageDisplayUrl': 'https://njsqxqyy.com/content/?644.html', 'width': 0, 'height': 0, 'thumbnail': None}], 'isFamilyFriendly': None}, 'videos': None}}
